metadata.name: Zoology #143
metadata.description:
Zoology is the branch of science dealing with animals. A species can be defined as the largest group of organisms in which any two individuals of the appropriate sex can produce fertile offspring - said the Artificial Intelligence who learnt it from Wiki.

Ai promt from Giorgio Ghisi's engravings (1520 — 1582)

I repainted and retouched some details and added colors and highlights.
